Package: FindPC
Title: FindPC: Find Number of Principal Components in Single-Cell Analysis
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Haotian", "Zhuang", email = "haotian.zhuang@duke.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Zhicheng", "Ji", email = "zhicheng.ji@duke.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: FindPC is a software tool including six methods to automatically select the number of principal components to retain based on the standard deviations explained by each PC. A major advantage of FindPC is that the only information required is a numeric vector of standard deviations explained by each PC.
